Data Attribution:

This project uses data from STEPBible (https://github.com/STEPBible/STEPBible-Data)
which is licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0).
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

STEPBible data includes:
- TBESG: Tyndale Brief lexicon of Extended Strongs for Greek
- TBESH: Tyndale Brief lexicon of Extended Strongs for Hebrew
- TAGNT: Translators Amalgamated Greek NT
- TAHOT: Translators Amalgamated Hebrew OT
- TIPNR: Translators Individualised Proper Names with all References
- TEGMC: Translators Expansion of Greek Morphology Codes
- TEHMC: Translators Expansion of Hebrew Morphology Codes

When using this software, please maintain attribution to STEPBible
for the underlying biblical data.
